{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "title",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# Infinity Canvas · Electron Split App\n**LEFT: Infinity Canvas · RIGHT: Detail (empty | node | codemap | source)**\n\nБаза: `luisfernando.infinite-canvas-0.1.5` → standalone Electron.\nСемантика: `langgraph.codemap`. AST: `alex-c` + `source/`.\n\n**UX-инвариант (корректировка):**\nодно окно, split: слева карта всегда; справа панель по selection.\nНе заменять canvas drill-down'ом.\n\nПлан агента: `AGENT_PLAN.md`",
      "x": -200,
      "y": -680,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "north_star",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 🎯 North Star\n\n1. Electron app, **не** VS Code extension.\n2. Open workspace → LLM → semantic `.canvas` на **LEFT**.\n3. **RIGHT** пустой, пока нет selection.\n4. Click node → RIGHT = content узла.\n5. Codemap action → RIGHT = deps (in) + derives (out) + locations.\n6. Location → RIGHT = source (monaco). LEFT не unmount.\n\n**DoD:** open → map LEFT ≤30s cache → click → RIGHT content/codemap → jump source.",
      "x": 280,
      "y": -520,
      "width": 400,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "sources",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 📦 Источники (read-only research)\n\n| Path | Роль |\n|------|------|\n| `luisfernando.infinite-canvas-0.1.5/` | Canvas UI, .canvas format, AI bridge |\n| `langgraph.codemap` | Схема semantic traces |\n| `alex-c.code-canvas-app-0.14.8/` | AST deps, xyflow, ast-grep |\n| `source/deobfuscated.js` + `source/*.js` | Webview modules code-canvas |\n| `cremniy_canvas.canvas` | Формат roadmap-промптов |\n\n**Правило:** не править vendor; только extract → own code.",
      "x": 740,
      "y": -520,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 260,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "phase1",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 🔍 Фаза 1 — Reverse Engineering источников",
      "x": -900,
      "y": -160,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "1_1",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 1.1 Infinite Canvas architecture\n\nРазобрать extension host + webview.\n\n**Файлы:**\n- `luisfernando.../out/extension.js`\n- `webview/main.js`\n- `webview/src/InfiniteCanvasSimple.js`\n- `AIManager.js`, `aiService.js`\n\n**Артефакт:** `docs/research/01-infinite-canvas.md`\n— message protocol, .canvas I/O, pan/zoom, AI hooks.\n\n**Промт агенту:**\n```\nИсследуй luisfernando.infinite-canvas-0.1.5.\nСоставь карту: activation, CanvasEditorProvider,\nwebview messaging (loadContent/save/loadFile),\nформат nodes/edges Obsidian-совместимый,\nкак AIManager генерит текст узлов.\nНе меняй код. Только markdown-отчёт +\nдиаграмма data flow Extension↔Webview↔.canvas.\n```",
      "x": -1180,
      "y": -60,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 380,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "1_2",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 1.2 Codemap schema (langgraph)\n\nФормализовать semantic graph schema.\n\n**Файл:** `langgraph.codemap`\n\nПоля: schemaVersion, traces[], locations[],\ntraceTextDiagram, mermaidDiagram, metadata.\n\n**Артефакт:** `docs/research/02-codemap-schema.md`\n+ TypeScript types `packages/schema/codemap.ts`\n\n**Промт агенту:**\n```\nПрочитай langgraph.codemap целиком.\nВыдели JSON-schema: root, Trace, Location,\nобязательные/опциональные поля, id-стратегии.\nОпиши mapping Trace→canvas node,\nLocation→drill-down card, edges между traces\nпо общим path/import.\nВыдай Zod-схему + пример минимального codemap\nна 2 traces. Код vendor не трогать.\n```",
      "x": -860,
      "y": -60,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 380,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "1_3",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 1.3 Code Canvas + deobfuscated\n\nИзвлечь AST/deps/layout паттерны.\n\n**Файлы:**\n- package.json (ast-grep, @xyflow/react, zustand)\n- source/deobfuscated.js + source/*.js\n- dist/extension.js (host commands)\n\n**Артефакт:** `docs/research/03-code-canvas-extract.md`\n— file graph, token refs, layout, ignore rules.\n\n**Промт агенту:**\n```\nИсследуй alex-c.code-canvas-app-0.14.8 и source/.\nНайди: как строится file/import graph,\nкак token references/deps edges,\nlayout algorithm hints, ignore patterns,\nwebview postMessage API (если видно).\nСписок capability checklist:\n[ ] folder tree [ ] open file on canvas\n[ ] deps edges [ ] token refs [ ] live watch.\nСсылки на module ids в source/*.js.\nБез reimplementation — только карта.\n```",
      "x": -540,
      "y": -60,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 380,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "1_4",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 1.4 Gap matrix & decisions\n\nСвести 3 источника → target architecture.\n\n**Артефакт:** `docs/research/04-gap-matrix.md`\n\n| Capability | infinite | codemap | code-canvas | Ours |\n| Canvas pan/zoom | ✅ | — | ✅ | own |\n| LLM semantic map | partial AI | ✅ schema | — | core |\n| AST deps | — | locations | ✅ | core |\n| Drill-down | — | traces | open file | core |\n\n**Промт:**\n```\nПо docs/research/01-03 составь gap-matrix\nи ADR: (1) Electron vs VS Code extension first,\n(2) canvas renderer: canvas2d vs xyflow/react,\n(3) LLM provider interface, (4) local AST engine.\nРекомендация + risks. Max 2 страницы.\n```",
      "x": -220,
      "y": -60,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 380,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "phase2",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 🧱 Фаза 2 — Electron + Split shell",
      "x": -900,
      "y": 420,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "2_1",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 2.1 Repo skeleton\n\n```\napps/desktop/\npackages/canvas-core/   # LEFT\npackages/detail-pane/   # RIGHT\npackages/schema|semantic|ast-graph|ipc|session\n```\n\n**Промт:** monorepo pnpm, electron-vite React TS,\npackages exports, README scripts. Vendor не копировать.\nСм. AGENT_PLAN.md §2.1",
      "x": -1180,
      "y": 520,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "2_2",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 2.2 Main + preload\n\nBrowserWindow, Open Folder, secure preload IPC.\nRenderer: workspace path + file count.\n\n**Промт:** см. AGENT_PLAN.md §2.2",
      "x": -860,
      "y": 520,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 220,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "2_3",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 2.3 ⭐ AppShell split LEFT|RIGHT\n\n**Критический UX-этап.**\n\n```\n[Toolbar]\n[LeftPane | Splitter | RightPane]\nrightMode: empty|content|codemap|source\n```\n\nLEFT placeholder → later canvas.\nRIGHT: empty hint · mock content · mock codemap.\nSplitter + persist leftRatio.\nEsc → empty. LEFT never navigates away.\n\n**Промт:** AGENT_PLAN.md §2.3\n**DoD:** mock click → RIGHT fills; LEFT stable.",
      "x": -540,
      "y": 520,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 380,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "2_4",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 2.4 Port canvas → LEFT + indexer\n\nPort InfiniteCanvasSimple → canvas-core in LeftPane.\nClick node → onSelect → RIGHT content.\n+ WorkspaceIndexer (ignore globs).\n\n**Промт:** AGENT_PLAN §2.4 + §2.5\nRoundtrip .canvas tests.",
      "x": -220,
      "y": 520,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 300,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "phase3",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 📐 Фаза 3 — Unified data model",
      "x": -900,
      "y": 960,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "3_1",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 3.1 Canvas document model\n\nObsidian-compatible + extensions:\n\n```ts\ntype ICNode = {\n  id, type: 'text'|'file'|'semantic'|'group',\n  x,y,width,height, color?,\n  text?, file?,\n  // extensions:\n  semantic?: { kind, summary, traceIds[] },\n  graph?: { path, symbol?, role: 'module'|'fn'|'class' }\n}\ntype ICEdge = {\n  id, fromNode, toNode, fromSide?, toSide?,\n  kind?: 'semantic'|'import'|'call'|'inherit'|'derives',\n  label?\n}\n```\n\n**Промт:**\n```\npackages/schema: Zod + TS types для\nCanvasDocument (Obsidian + IC extensions),\nвалидатор, migrateLegacy().\nТесты: cremniy_canvas.canvas парсится;\nрасширенные поля roundtrip; strip unknown OK.\n```",
      "x": -1180,
      "y": 1060,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 380,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "3_2",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 3.2 Codemap model\n\n1:1 с langgraph.codemap + normalizer.\n\n```ts\nCodemap {\n  schemaVersion, id, stableId, title,\n  metadata, traces: Trace[],\n  description?, mermaidDiagram?\n}\nTrace { id, title, description,\n  locations: Location[],\n  traceTextDiagram?, traceGuide? }\nLocation { id, path, lineNumber,\n  lineContent?, title?, description? }\n```\n\n**Промт:**\n```\npackages/schema/codemap.ts из langgraph.codemap.\nparseCodemap(), validate(), toCanvasProjection()\n(traces→nodes, heuristic edges).\nGolden test: load langgraph.codemap →\nN nodes == traces.length.\n```",
      "x": -860,
      "y": 1060,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 360,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "3_3",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 3.3 Dependency graph model\n\n```ts\nDepGraph {\n  nodes: Map<path|symbolId, DepNode>\n  edges: DepEdge[] // import|call|type|export\n}\nDepNode { id, path, name, kind, exports[] }\nDepEdge { from, to, kind, loc? }\n// derived:\nincoming(id), outgoing(id), subgraph(id, depth)\n```\n\n**Промт:**\n```\npackages/schema/dep-graph.ts + pure helpers:\nincoming, outgoing, egoNetwork(center, depth),\ntopologicalLayers (DAG only).\nФикстура 5 файлов A→B→C. Тесты helpers.\n```",
      "x": -540,
      "y": 1060,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 340,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "3_4",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 3.4 Session state (incl. split UI)\n\n```ts\nui: {\n  selectedNodeId,\n  rightMode: 'empty'|'content'|'codemap'|'source',\n  leftRatio,\n  source?: { path, line }\n}\n```\n\nCache `.infinity-canvas/`. IPC session:get/patch.\n\n**Промт:** AGENT_PLAN §3.4",
      "x": -220,
      "y": 1060,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 320,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "phase4",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 🤖 Фаза 4 — LLM Semantic Map (on project open)",
      "x": 200,
      "y": -160,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4_1",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 4.1 Context packer\n\nСобрать prompt context без отправки всего repo:\n- tree (depth-limited)\n- package.json / README / entrypoints\n- top-N files by centrality (import degree later)\n- budgets: tokens / max files\n\n**Промт:**\n```\npackages/semantic/contextPacker.ts:\ninput FileMeta[] + optional DepGraph skeleton,\noutput ContextPack { tree, manifests, samples[] }\nс hard budget (e.g. 80k chars).\nПриоритет: README, package.json, src/index*,\nmain modules. Тест на fixtures/mini-project.\n```",
      "x": 80,
      "y": -60,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 320,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4_2",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 4.2 LLM provider interface\n\n```ts\ninterface LLMProvider {\n  complete(req: {\n    system, user, jsonSchema?\n  }): Promise<string>\n}\n// OpenRouter | OpenAI | Ollama | Mock\n```\nConfig: API key в secure store Electron.\n\n**Промт:**\n```\npackages/semantic/providers/*\nLLMProvider interface + MockProvider\n(deterministic JSON map) + OpenRouterProvider.\nEnv: INFINITY_LLM_API_KEY, model name.\nRetry/timeout. Не логировать secrets.\n```",
      "x": 400,
      "y": -60,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 300,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4_3",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 4.3 Semantic map prompt + parser\n\nSystem prompt: вернуть JSON CanvasDocument\n(semantic nodes) в духе langgraph traces:\n- 5–20 nodes (modules/concepts)\n- edges kind=semantic\n- summary 1–3 sentences\n- optional file anchors[]\n\nValidate Zod → fallback layout.\n\n**Промт:**\n```\nРеализуй buildSemanticMap(pack, llm):\n1) system+user prompt templates\n2) parse JSON (fence-strip)\n3) validate CanvasDocument\n4) assign x,y grid if missing\n5) return map + diagnostics\nGolden: MockProvider → valid canvas\ncompatible with infinite-canvas loader.\nPrompt must mirror codemap philosophy:\nnodes = structural invariants / subsystems.\n```",
      "x": 720,
      "y": -60,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 360,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4_4",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 4.4 Orchestrate → LEFT map, RIGHT empty\n\nonWorkspaceOpen → semantic map → **LEFT only**.\nRIGHT remains empty until selection.\nProgress + cancel + cache.\n\n**Промт:** AGENT_PLAN §4.4",
      "x": 1040,
      "y": -60,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4_5",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 4.5 Incremental refresh\n\nКнопки: Regenerate Map / Update delta.\nDelta: only changed files summaries → LLM merge.\n\n**Промт:**\n```\nДобавь semanticMap:regenerate и :patch.\nPatch mode: diff file list vs previous cacheKey,\nLLM merge instruction preserve stable node ids\nwhere possible. Тест Mock merge keeps id=auth.\n```",
      "x": 1360,
      "y": -60,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 260,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "phase5",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 🎨 Фаза 5 — LEFT map UX + RIGHT content",
      "x": 200,
      "y": 420,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "5_1",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 5.1 Semantic node chrome\n\nВизуал узла:\n- title + kind badge (module/layer/flow)\n- 2-line summary\n- counters: files · deps\n- color by layer\n\n**Промт:**\n```\nВ canvas-core renderer: SemanticNodeView.\nДанные из node.semantic. Hover outline,\nselected glow. Не ломать text/file nodes\nиз Obsidian format.\n```",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 520,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "5_2",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 5.2 Semantic edges & layout\n\nkind=semantic: dashed/colored.\nAuto-layout: hierarchical (sugiyama-lite)\nили force-directed fallback.\nFit-to-view after load.\n\n**Промт:**\n```\npackages/canvas-core/layout:\nhierarchicalLayout(nodes, edges) + fitView.\nApply after semantic map load.\nEdges: stroke by kind; label optional.\nTest: no overlapping centers on 10-node chain.\n```",
      "x": 380,
      "y": 520,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "5_3",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 5.3 Click → RIGHT content (not replace LEFT)\n\nSingle click:\n  selectedNodeId + rightMode='content'\nRIGHT ContentView: title, summary, files[],\n  [Codemap] [files]\ntext node → show text; file node → preview.\n\nEsc → rightMode='empty'\n**LEFT stays mounted.**\n\n**Промт:** AGENT_PLAN §5.3",
      "x": 680,
      "y": 520,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 320,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "5_4",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 5.4 Toolbar & empty/error states\n\nToolbar: Open Folder · Regenerate ·\nZoom fit · Toggle minimap.\nErrors: LLM fail → Mock/offline map + toast.\n\n**Промт:**\n```\nUI shell: toolbar, status bar (workspace,\nmap age, node count), error banner with Retry.\nOffline: load last cache or skeleton map\nfrom folder tree only (no LLM).\n```",
      "x": 980,
      "y": 520,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "phase6",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 🧬 Фаза 6 — AST / Dependency engine",
      "x": 200,
      "y": 900,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "6_1",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 6.1 Language adapters\n\nMVP languages: TS/JS first (import/export).\nLater: Python, Go via ast-grep langs.\n\n```ts\ninterface LangAdapter {\n  extensions: string[]\n  extract(file, src): { imports, exports, symbols }\n}\n```\n\n**Промт:**\n```\npackages/ast-graph/adapters/ts-js.ts:\nparse imports/exports (typescript compiler API\nили lightweight regex+acorn — выбрать и ADR).\nFixture multi-file project. Snapshot extract().\nНе тащить весь @ast-grep пока не нужно.\n```",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 1000,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 340,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "6_2",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 6.2 Build DepGraph\n\nResolve relative/absolute imports → edges.\nHandle index files, package.json exports\nbest-effort.\n\n**Промт:**\n```\nbuildDepGraph(root, files, adapters):\nDepGraph. Resolve paths, skip externals\n(node_modules) as external nodes optional.\nAPI: getEgo(path, depth=1|2).\nTest chain A imports B imports C.\n```",
      "x": 400,
      "y": 1000,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 300,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "6_3",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 6.3 Symbol-level edges (optional MVP+)\n\ncall/type references inside module\n(вдохновение code-canvas token refs).\n\n**Промт:**\n```\nSpike: для одного TS файла извлечь\nfunction calls to local imports.\nЕсли >2 дня — mark backlog, ship file-level only.\nДокументировать в ADR.\n```",
      "x": 720,
      "y": 1000,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 260,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "6_4",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 6.4 Index cache & watch\n\nIncremental re-parse on file change.\nchokidar in main process.\n\n**Промт:**\n```\nDepGraphService: full build + applyFileChange.\nEmit depGraph:updated. Cache serialized graph.\nIgnore noise (same as indexer).\n```",
      "x": 1020,
      "y": 1000,
