      "text": "### 7.1 Ego-network → RIGHT CodemapView\n\nfromSemanticNode → deps in + derives out.\nRender **in RIGHT only** (lists or mini-graph).\nLEFT semantic map untouched (+ highlight).\n\n**Промт:** AGENT_PLAN §7.1",
