      "text": "### 7.2 Codemap JSON (langgraph-like)\n\ntoCodemap → traces/locations.\nSave codemaps/{nodeId}.codemap\nRIGHT: trace list + expand locations.\n\n**Промт:** AGENT_PLAN §7.2",
      "x": 400,
