      "text": "### 7.3 RIGHT-only mode stack\n\nStack **inside RIGHT**:\nempty ↔ content ↔ codemap ↔ source\nBack btn + breadcrumb in RIGHT header.\nNo full-window navigation.\n\n**Промт:** AGENT_PLAN §7.3",
      "x": 720,
