    {
      "id": "phase8",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 🔗 Фаза 8 — LLM enrich codemap (optional depth)",
      "x": 1620,
      "y": -160,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8_1",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 8.1 Trace generation prompt\n\nПо ego-network + file samples LLM пишет\ntraces как в langgraph.codemap\n(title, guide, locations must exist in graph).\n\n**Промт:**\n```\nenrichCodemap(structural, llm):\nLLM returns traces[]; filter locations\nnot in allowed set; merge with structural.\nMockProvider test preserves valid paths only.\n```",
      "x": 1500,
      "y": -60,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8_2",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 8.2 Trace UI on canvas\n\nMode: highlight path of selected trace\n(sequential glow edges/nodes).\nPanel: traceGuide markdown.\n\n**Промт:**\n```\nTraceHighlighter: given location order,\nselect nodes/edges and pulse animation.\nMarkdown render traceGuide (sanitize).\n```",
      "x": 1820,
      "y": -60,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 260,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8_3",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 8.3 Export / import\n\nExport: .canvas + .codemap zip.\nImport langgraph.codemap as read-only overlay\n(для research mode на vendor).\n\n**Промт:**\n```\nCommands: Export Research Bundle,\nImport Codemap. Load langgraph.codemap\nfrom workspace root as demo overlay.\n```",
      "x": 2120,
      "y": -60,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 260,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "phase9",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## ⚡ Фаза 9 — Perf, privacy, polish",
      "x": 1620,
      "y": 320,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "9_1",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 9.1 Performance budgets\n\n- Index 10k files < 3s\n- DepGraph TS project 2k files < 15s\n- Canvas 500 nodes 60fps pan\nVirtualize if needed.\n\n**Промт:**\n```\nДобавь perf marks + simple benchmark CLI.\nDocument numbers in docs/perf.md.\nIf canvas lag: canvas2d culling offscreen nodes.\n```",
      "x": 1500,
      "y": 420,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "9_2",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 9.2 Privacy controls\n\n- Toggle: send code samples to LLM yes/no\n- Redact secrets (API keys patterns)\n- Local-only mode (Ollama)\n\n**Промт:**\n```\nSettings UI: privacy mode, provider, model.\ncontextPacker redacts /key|secret|token/i.\nLocal-only disables cloud providers.\n```",
      "x": 1800,
      "y": 420,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 260,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "9_3",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 9.3 UX polish\n\nMinimap, search nodes, keyboard map,\ntheme dark/light, welcome tour.\n\n**Промт:**\n```\nMinimap + Ctrl+F node search + shortcuts help.\nPersist window bounds. Splash/welcome\nexplaining semantic→codemap flow.\n```",
      "x": 2100,
      "y": 420,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 260,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "9_4",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 9.4 Resilience\n\nCrash recovery, corrupt cache repair,\nLLM schema repair loop (1 retry).\n\n**Промт:**\n```\nCache versioning; on parse fail quarantine\n+ rebuild. LLM invalid JSON → repair prompt once.\nLog to .infinity-canvas/logs/.\n```",
      "x": 2400,
      "y": 420,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 260,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "phase10",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 🚀 Фаза 10 — Ship: tests, package, docs",
      "x": 1620,
      "y": 800,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "10_1",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 10.1 E2E split path\n\nSmoke: open fixture → LEFT map (mock) →\nclick node → RIGHT content → Codemap →\nlocations > 0. vitest + playwright.\n\n**Промт:** AGENT_PLAN §10.1",
      "x": 1500,
      "y": 900,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 260,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "10_2",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 10.2 Packaging\n\nelectron-builder AppImage/dmg/nsis.\nAuto-update optional later.\n\n**Промт:**\n```\nelectron-builder config, icons, version from\npackage.json. Document release checklist.\n```",
      "x": 1800,
      "y": 900,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 240,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "10_3",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 10.3 Documentation\n\n- ARCHITECTURE.md (diagrams)\n- USER_GUIDE.md (semantic→codemap)\n- AGENT_RUNBOOK.md (phase prompts order)\n- RESEARCH.md links to docs/research/*\n\n**Промт:**\n```\nСгенерируй docs из фактического кода.\nAGENT_RUNBOOK: одна фаза = один PR,\nDoD checklist per phase, no skipping.\n```",
      "x": 2100,
      "y": 900,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "10_4",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### 10.4 Research mode demo\n\nВстроенный demo: открыть этот repo\nast-canvas как workspace — semantic map\nпо 3 vendor folders + import langgraph.codemap.\n\n**Промт:**\n```\nDemo script + fixture config for ast-canvas\nworkspace. Verify user can explore\ninfinite-canvas vs code-canvas vs codemap\nwithout leaving the app.\n```",
      "x": 2400,
      "y": 900,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "agent_rules",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 🤖 Правила агента (анти-съезд)\n\n1. Читать `AGENT_PLAN.md` + этот canvas.\n2. **Layout:** LEFT canvas always · RIGHT reactive pane.\n3. Одна фаза/этап = один PR. Не skip DoD.\n4. Vendor read-only.\n5. Schema/tests before fancy UI.\n6. Mock LLM в dev/CI.\n7. North Star: open→LEFT map→click→RIGHT content/codemap.\n8. Atomic commits: stage id (2_3, 5_3…).\n9. File-level deps first; symbols later.\n10. `docs/STATUS.md` после этапа.",
      "x": 1620,
      "y": 1300,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 360,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "dod_global",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## ✅ Global DoD (MVP)\n\n- [ ] Electron, **split LEFT|RIGHT**\n- [ ] Semantic map on LEFT (LLM/mock)\n- [ ] No selection → RIGHT empty\n- [ ] Click node → RIGHT content\n- [ ] Codemap → deps + derivatives\n- [ ] Source @ line in RIGHT\n- [ ] Splitter ratio persisted\n- [ ] Cache / offline mock\n- [ ] Tests + README\n\n**Non-goals:** drill-down replace LEFT, VS Code ext, webGL.",
      "x": 2100,
      "y": 1300,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 340,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "flow",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 🔁 Runtime + Layout\n\n```\n┌─ Toolbar ──────────────────────────┐\n│ LEFT: Infinity Canvas │ RIGHT: Pane │\n│ semantic map (always) │ empty       │\n│                       │ content     │\n│                       │ codemap     │\n│                       │ source      │\n└───────────────────────┴─────────────┘\n\nOpen Folder → map → LEFT\nClick node → RIGHT content\nCodemap → RIGHT deps+derives\nLocation → RIGHT monaco\nEsc → RIGHT empty\n```",
      "x": 2500,
      "y": 1300,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 340,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "layout_ui",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 🖥️ UI Layout (locked)\n\n```\nLEFT 60%              RIGHT 40%\n┌──────────────────┬─────────────────┐\n│ Infinity Canvas  │ Detail Pane     │\n│ semantic map     │ empty           │\n│ always visible   │ node content    │\n│                  │ codemap         │\n│                  │ source/monaco   │\n└──────────────────┴─────────────────┘\n     resizable splitter\n```\n\nPackage: `detail-pane` = RIGHT.\nPackage: `canvas-core` = LEFT.\nПлан: AGENT_PLAN.md",
      "x": 280,
      "y": -820,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "1"
    }
  ],
